{"tid":18604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（689）品客陣營中人：唔做縮龜頭","createTime":"2016-12-02T11:26:23.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T15:11:13.000Z","uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9b7fb4049acfd8965ce293abcd66cc18ac51436c","tid":18604,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T11:26:23.000Z","msg":"特首選舉將近，《經濟日報》「傅流螢」專欄周五指，港澳辦主任王光亞日前私下見了曾俊華，並向他表明，不支持其參選特首，與早前《星島》政情專欄引述「接近北京人士」消息相同；而《信報》政情專欄「余錦賢」則引述消息指，曾俊華<span style=\"color: red;\">訪京前已對「探路」結果心中有數，但「如果以為佢會做縮頭烏龜，係太睇小佢</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n「余錦賢」專欄稱，目前各方大打心理戰是預期之內，因中央最高層未有最終決定，文中又引述接近曾俊華陣營人士指，「無論點佢都會照去馬」；《香港01》早前亦發佈獨家「接近北京」消息，指曾俊華日前訪京為參選尋求「開綠燈」，而中央的答覆是「不會公開支持他參選，但亦不會禁止」，曾已決定「去馬」，預計在選委會選舉結束後翌日(12日)，將正式向中央及梁振英呈辭，待中央回覆批准後隨即宣布參選特首。<br />\n<br />\n報道又引述<span style=\"color: red;\">消息人士指「曾俊華的競選工程已準備就緒，而且評估過有足夠勝算</span>」，但認為不宜剛從北京回港就立即宣布參選，故選擇在月中選委會選舉結束後宣布消息，並指這是目前能掌握的消息，未知曾最終會否隨着形勢變化而改變部署。<br />\n<br />\n另外，《明報》亦引述曾營中人分析指，近日曾俊華遇「紅燈」的消息，或多或少影響一些支持者的決心，指曾「將於日內反擊」，爭取曝光機會，在公開場合回應近日種種不利他參選特首的傳聞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161202&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=55993228\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161202%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D55993228&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdAT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=b9e64361\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161202%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D55993228&h=327f6920\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161202&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=55993228</a>"},{"pid":"059085ddf57d708d9c1970ec7fb187da6374c149","tid":18604,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T11:27:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 縮頭龜<br />\n<br />\n打撚錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e723ca90d3c6ee32af1eb3052b3aa4a606187d","tid":18604,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T11:47:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 縮頭龜<br />\n<br />\n打撚錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑死我"},{"pid":"4c71fcafd94173397366e98e0f3f6b9c10e89dec","tid":18604,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T11:49:37.000Z","msg":"仲諗緊咩叫縮龜頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc816cc0530292a86022e6030f8e09f248c1a143","tid":18604,"uid":10611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T11:59:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"174cf510963edf960b06ec714b9cea7516e7df10","tid":18604,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T14:11:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1de1ff3ba7ab75b6eac707afa24457775ccd012","tid":18604,"uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T14:13:54.000Z","msg":"快撚 d 選啦，唔係你俾 689 dq 埋呀柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f4edacea09c643186a69a63e4ecb2b51886e2d","tid":18604,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T15:11:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>快撚 d 選啦，唔係你俾 689 dq 埋呀柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n宣完誓<br />\n監誓人接受左都可以DQ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}